Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.31,0:21:37.10,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}It's been so long since we left our home behind
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.15,0:21:43.36,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Drifting on the Milky Way almost every single day
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.36,0:21:46.82,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Where am I supposed to go ?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.41,0:21:49.91,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}What're we really looking for ?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.24,0:21:55.00,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Stumbling in the darkness, cold and lost
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.08,0:22:01.88,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}But a ray of hope still exists in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.67,0:22:07.38,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Rain or shine, always chase the dream
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.43,0:22:11.51,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Someday, we'll fly across the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.72,0:22:14.98,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Never fearing anything
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.14,0:22:19.77,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}We'll promise that"we'll go on ! "
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.90,0:22:23.94,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Even if you're against the wind,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.07,0:22:25.44,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Never stop !
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.65,0:22:27.20,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Don't look back !
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.32,0:22:32.62,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}We'll one day rise above it all (never give up)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.66,0:22:36.45,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Who cares if the going's tough
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.54,0:22:38.00,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Never think !
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.16,0:22:39.87,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Keep pushing on !
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.13,0:22:46.97,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}We can find our promised land
