Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.36,0:21:46.82,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我欲去往何處
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.41,0:21:49.91,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我在追尋何物
