Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.78,0:00:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\pos(784.5,987)}drill pipe
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.20,0:00:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,磁性固體正常 周邊環境變化也未超出基準
